OH, MY MOTHER'S GONNA THINK
THIS IS MY FAULT.

13:53.200 --> 13:54.200
WHY IS THAT?

13:55.700 --> 13:58.100
WHEN I GOT FIRED, SHE SAID
SHE DIDN'T WANT ME TO COME HOME

13:59.400 --> 14:01.300
AND NOT TO BOTHER HER ANYMORE.

14:01.400 --> 14:03.800
SHE DIDN'T EVEN WANT TO HEAR
MY SIDE OF THE STORY.

14:04.800 --> 14:06.900
"BLAME ROGER FIRST."

14:07.100 --> 14:08.800
THAT'S HER MANTRO.

14:09.000 --> 14:10.300
OR MOTTO OR WHATEVER.

14:10.400 --> 14:11.800
THAT'S TERRIBLE.

14:12.800 --> 14:14.500
THAT IS SO UNFAIR.

14:15.100 --> 14:16.600
WHEN THE REST OF THE WORLD
LETS YOU DOWN,

14:16.700 --> 14:19.200
YOU SHOULD ALWAYS BE ABLE
TO COUNT ON YOUR MOTHER.

14:20.300 --> 14:22.900
SHE'S SUPPOSED TO LOVE YOU
NO MATTER WHAT.

14:25.800 --> 14:29.100
AND RIGHT NOW,
THERE'S ANOTHER LITTLE GIRL...

14:30.300 --> 14:33.300
THAT I'M SURE WOULD LIKE
TO TALK TO HER MOTHER AND CAN'T.

14:33.800 --> 14:35.900
MIGHT HAVE HEARD ABOUT HER
ON THE NEWS.

14:36.300 --> 14:38.000
LITTLE GIRL WENT MISSING TODAY.

14:38.600 --> 14:41.700
I'M SURE HER MOTHER IS JUST
DESPERATE TO HEAR HER VOICE.

14:42.400 --> 14:45.800
AND I-I FEEL STRONGLY THAT
YOU CAN HELP US WITH THIS,

14:45.900 --> 14:47.600
BECAUSE YOU WERE DRIVING AROUND

14:47.700 --> 14:50.600
IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD
WHERE SHE WENT MISSING.

14:50.700 --> 14:53.300
<i>SO IF YOU KNOW ANYTHING</i>
<i>OR YOU SAW ANYTHING,</i>

14:53.800 --> 14:55.500
I'D REALLY LIKE TO KNOW.

14:57.700 --> 14:58.700
ROGER.

15:03.100 --> 15:05.500
YOU KNOW WHERE I MIGHT FIND
THIS LITTLE GIRL?

15:25.700 --> 15:27.200
WHAT LITTLE GIRL?

15:33.700 --> 15:35.600
HER NAME IS RUBY WILLIAMS.

15:37.300 --> 15:38.800
SHE'S 8 YEARS OLD.

15:40.500 --> 15:42.400
SHE LIKES TO PLAY THE VIOLIN.

15:48.600 --> 15:50.700
AND THIS AFTERNOON,
ON HER WAY HOME FROM SCHOOL,

15:50.800 --> 15:52.300
SHE WAS ABDUCTED.

15:53.000 --> 15:55.900
SHE WAS IN YOUR VAN!

15:58.000 --> 16:01.000
IF SOMETHING HAPPENED,
I WANT TO HELP YOU FIGURE THIS OUT.

16:01.600 --> 16:04.200
THIS IS YOUR CHANCE
TO EXPLAIN YOURSELF.

16:12.200 --> 16:13.700
I WANT A LAWYER.

16:17.900 --> 16:19.100
INTERVIEW OVER.

16:22.700 --> 16:24.100
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

16:37.800 --> 16:39.800
FRITZ, ARE WE ANY CLOSER
TO FINDING THE GIRL?

16:39.900 --> 16:41.200
HANG ON, WILL.

16:42.100 --> 16:44.200
DIDN'T GET ANYTHING FROM THE VAN
OR THE APARTMENT?

16:44.600 --> 16:46.800
NO. NO.
HE'S LAWYERED UP.

16:46.900 --> 16:48.700
AND I NEED SOMETHING
THAT TIES HIM TO RUBY WILLIAMS,

16:48.800 --> 16:51.200
OTHER THAN THE TESTIMONY
OF A GERMAN SHEPHERD.

16:54.000 --> 16:55.700
DON'T LOOK AT ME LIKE THAT.

16:56.600 --> 16:58.700
AND HOW WOULD YOU LIKE ME
TO LOOK AT YOU?

16:59.800 --> 17:01.400
DON'T JUDGE ME.

17:02.900 --> 17:04.700
I KNOW THAT LOOK.

17:05.500 --> 17:09.000
<i>WELL, YOU KNOW, I KNOW A LITTLE</i>
<i>SOMETHING ABOUT LOOKS, TOO.</i>

17:09.599 --> 17:10.700
LOOKING AT YOU...

17:11.200 --> 17:13.200
YOU KNOW SOMETHING
ABOUT THIS LITTLE GIRL.

17:22.599 --> 17:24.200
SHE'S NOT <i>THAT</i>  LITTLE.

17:27.200 --> 17:28.300
OH, REALLY?

17:31.400 --> 17:33.200
YOU SEE, EVERYONE...

17:33.700 --> 17:35.400
PRETENDS KIDS...

17:36.400 --> 17:38.400
DON'T WANT SEX.

17:39.600 --> 17:40.800
BUT THEY DO.

17:43.600 --> 17:45.600
YOU REMEMBER WHEN YOU WERE A KID?

17:47.500 --> 17:49.100
THAT'S ALL YOU THOUGHT ABOUT.

17:49.900 --> 17:51.500
THERE'S NOTHING WRONG WITH IT.

17:53.000 --> 17:54.600
IT'S BIOLOGY.

17:56.800 --> 17:58.200
AND BESIDES...

18:00.500 --> 18:02.300
BLACK GIRLS ARE DIFFERENT.

18:06.000 --> 18:07.300
IS THAT RIGHT?

18:10.000 --> 18:11.300
I MEAN, LOOK AT HER.

18:14.100 --> 18:17.300
BLACK GIRLS ARE WAY MORE
SEXUALLY MATURE THAN WHITE GIRLS.

18:21.000 --> 18:23.000
THAT'S WHY THEY HAVE KIDS SO YOUNG.

18:25.600 --> 18:28.400
YOU PROBABLY GREW UP
SWIMMING IN BLACK ASS.

18:30.500 --> 18:32.100
IT'S THE WAY THEY WALK.

18:36.400 --> 18:38.700
SHAKE...SHAKE...

18:39.000 --> 18:40.800
SHAKIN' THEIR THING.

18:47.800 --> 18:48.800
KILL THE FEED, BUZZ.

18:48.900 --> 18:50.800
- BUT THE CHIEF SAID NO.
- I SAID KILL IT!

18:58.900 --> 19:01.700
DO <i>NOT</i>  LEAVE THIS ROOM!

19:04.200 --> 19:05.600
WHY NOT?

19:06.700 --> 19:08.700
BECAUSE SERGEANT GABRIEL...

19:09.900 --> 19:12.300
IS ABOUT TO MAKE A BREAK IN THE CASE.

19:16.500 --> 19:19.200
NO, DETECTIVE DANIS, DON'T SAY
ANYTHING TO THE FAMILY YET.

19:19.300 --> 19:20.600
COULD BE A HOAX.

19:21.600 --> 19:24.700
NO, NO. HE WOULDN'T TELL ME.
HE TOLD SERGEANT GABRIEL.

19:25.500 --> 19:27.600
YES, IT <i>IS</i>  AMAZING.

19:28.300 --> 19:30.200
UH, IT DOESN'T MATTER
WHO HE TOLD -- WE KNOW.

19:30.300 --> 19:33.200
SEND FOUR BLACK-AND-WHITES
TO THE VERMONT CANYON ENTRANCE

19:33.300 --> 19:35.200
BY THE PAY PHONES
AT THE REST AREA.

19:36.200 --> 19:38.100
AND, UH, SEND THE K-9s.

19:38.300 --> 19:39.200
THANK YOU.

19:40.000 --> 19:41.900
SERGEANT GABRIEL,
JUST TO BE CLEAR --

19:42.000 --> 19:44.300
ROGER SAID??
THAT HE LEFT RUBY AT THE PARK.

19:44.400 --> 19:46.900
HE DIDN'T SAY THAT SHE WAS DEAD.
IS THAT RIGHT?

19:58.700 --> 20:00.500
WHERE ARE THE PHONES?
WHERE ARE THE PHONES?!

20:15.700 --> 20:16.600
RUBY!

20:18.700 --> 20:19.500
RUBY!

20:21.900 --> 20:22.500
DAMN IT!

20:57.900 --> 20:59.400
???

22:13.300 --> 22:14.200
IN MY OFFICE.

22:21.100 --> 22:22.000
WHAT DID YOU DO?

22:22.800 --> 22:24.800
WE FOUND HER, DIDN'T WE?
DOESN'T MATTER WHAT I DID.

22:26.200 --> 22:27.300
NOTHING MATTERS MORE.

22:29.600 --> 22:31.400
ROGER STIMPLE
DIDN'T LOOK LIKE THAT

22:31.800 --> 22:33.100
WHEN I LEFT
THE INTERVIEW ROOM.

22:34.100 --> 22:35.700
SO, I NEED TO KNOW,
SERGEANT --

22:37.100 --> 22:38.400
DID YOU BEAT
THE SUSPECT?

22:38.400 --> 22:39.300
HE DESERVED IT.

22:40.700 --> 22:42.800
THAT IS NOT SOMETHING
THAT YOU GET TO DECIDE

22:43.300 --> 22:45.700
ON YOUR OWN
IN AN INTERVIEW ROOM

22:46.100 --> 22:47.000
WITH YOUR FISTS.

22:47.000 --> 22:49.700
ARE YOU SERIOUSLY
TAKING HIS SIDE?

22:50.400 --> 22:52.800
HE KILLED HER.
I GOT A CONFESSION.

22:52.800 --> 22:54.100
<i>YOU GOT AN ADMISSION.</i>

22:55.300 --> 22:57.200
ROGER TOLD YOU
WHERE TO FIND HER.

22:58.800 --> 23:01.100
NOT THAT HE TOOK HER,
NOT THAT HE KILLED HER.

23:01.400 --> 23:03.700
AND SINCE YOU BEAT
THAT ADMISSION OUT OF HIM,

23:03.700 --> 23:05.100
A JURY WON'T BE ABLE
TO HEAR IT ANYWAY.

23:09.700 --> 23:14.000
I PROMISED THAT MOTHER I WAS
GONNA BRING HER DAUGHTER HOME.

23:14.300 --> 23:16.200
AND THAT'S EXACTLY
WHAT I WAS TRYING TO DO.

23:16.200 --> 23:18.200
YOU COMMITTED
A CRIMINAL ACT.

23:21.400 --> 23:24.600
WHEN ROGER GETS A LAWYER
AND TELLS HIM WHAT YOU DID

23:25.800 --> 23:27.400
AND I.A.
HEARS HIS COMPLAINT...

23:30.600 --> 23:31.600
WHAT ABOUT YOUR FUTURE?

23:41.300 --> 23:43.200
WELL, WHAT DO YOU --
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO DO NOW?

23:48.400 --> 23:49.100
JUST GO HOME.

23:51.100 --> 23:52.300
????

24:12.500 --> 24:14.400
<i>YOU PROBABLY GREW UP
SWIMMING IN BLACK ASS.</i>

24:16.000 --> 24:17.000
<i>IT'S THE WAY THEY WALK.</i>

24:19.300 --> 24:21.500
<i>SHAKE...SHAKE...</i>

24:22.100 --> 24:23.400
<i>SHAKIN' THEIR THING.</i>

24:35.500 --> 24:37.000
BUZZ, WHY DID YOU STOP
THE TAPING?

24:38.000 --> 24:40.200
I THOUGHT
WHEN YOU, UH, LEFT THE ROOM,

24:40.200 --> 24:41.200
THE INTERVIEW WAS OVER.

24:42.300 --> 24:43.800
I HAVE MADE MYSELF
PERFECTLY CLEAR --

24:44.200 --> 24:45.700
UNLESS I STOP THAT TAPE
MYSELF,

24:45.700 --> 24:48.000
IT STAYS ON AS LONG AS
THE SUSPECT IS IN THE ROOM.

24:48.000 --> 24:48.800
CHIEF...

24:51.000 --> 24:51.900
I KILLED THE FEED.

24:52.600 --> 24:53.200
WHY?

24:54.500 --> 24:55.300
BECAUSE...

24:57.000 --> 24:58.400
I THOUGHT
IT WAS A GOOD IDEA.

25:12.900 --> 25:14.900
LIEUTENANT, I WANT YOU
TO TAKE CHARGE OF THE PRISONER.

25:15.200 --> 25:17.900
MAKE SURE HE'S FED.
AND GETS MEDICAL ATTENTION IF HE NEEDS IT.

25:20.500 --> 25:22.200
WE DON'T HAVE TO BOOK HIM
OR LET HIM SEE HIS LAWYER

25:22.200 --> 25:25.000
UNTIL HE'S ARRAIGNED, WHICH
MEANS WE HAVE LESS THAN 43 HOURS

25:25.100 --> 25:27.000
TO TIE HIM TO RUBY'S MURDER
SOME OTHER WAY.

25:28.600 --> 25:31.600
I WANT THE SQUAD WORKING,
BUT NO ONE SEES THIS TAPE

25:32.500 --> 25:34.400
OR KNOWS ABOUT
WHAT SERGEANT GABRIEL HAS DONE.

25:35.000 --> 25:36.400
HAVE I MADE MYSELF
VERY CLEAR?

25:36.500 --> 25:37.200
YES, MA'AM.

25:56.800 --> 25:57.400
THANKS.

25:59.400 --> 26:00.000
HEY.

26:00.200 --> 26:03.900
LISTEN, YOUR INSTINCTS
ABOUT ROGER'S SECOND CAR WERE RIGHT ON.

26:04.600 --> 26:06.600
WE FOUND A REPORT
ON A '77 MERCURY COUGAR

26:06.600 --> 26:09.600
JUST LIKE ROGER'S --
SAME BLUE PAINT ON THE BUMPER --

26:10.000 --> 26:12.800
TIED TO TWO SEPARATE ABDUCTIONS
FIVE YEARS AGO,

26:12.800 --> 26:15.600
BEFORE OUR GUY WENT TO JAIL
ON THAT SEXUAL-BATTERY CHARGE.

26:16.600 --> 26:20.100
TWO GIRLS, AFRICAN-AMERICAN,
AGES 9 AND 11.

26:20.400 --> 26:21.300
THEY WERE NEVER FOUND.

26:22.300 --> 26:24.000
SO RUBY WASN'T
HIS FIRST VICTIM.

26:24.500 --> 26:27.800
WELL,LAST FEW YEARS ON PAROLE
MUST HAVE BEEN A COOLING-OFF PERIOD.

26:27.900 --> 26:30.900
BUT HE JUST LOST HIS JOB, AND
YOU SAID HIS FAMILY CUT HIM OFF?

26:30.900 --> 26:33.800
HE'S GOT SOME KIND
OF A...MOTHER THING.

26:34.400 --> 26:36.700
YEAH, JUST THE KIND OF
STRESSOR EVENTS TO SET HIM OFF.

26:37.300 --> 26:39.600
I SHOULD HAVE NEVER LEFT GABRIEL
ALONE IN THAT ROOM.

26:42.000 --> 26:43.700
I SAW HOW MAD HE WAS.

26:45.700 --> 26:47.000
I KNEW HE WAS UPSET.

26:48.200 --> 26:49.300
YOU TOLD POPE ABOUT IT
YET?

26:49.900 --> 26:50.600
NO.

26:52.400 --> 26:53.800
I'M STILL LOOKING
FOR A WAY OUT.

26:54.300 --> 26:57.900
WELL, YOU TIE ROGER STIMPLE
TO THESE OTHER MISSING GIRLS...

27:04.800 --> 27:06.100
IT'S OKAY. IT'S OKAY.

27:10.200 --> 27:11.600
DETECTIVE.
YOU'RE WORKING LATE.

27:12.000 --> 27:13.400
UH, YES.

27:13.400 --> 27:15.200
WE FOUND OUT
THAT THE LANDSCAPING FIRM

27:15.200 --> 27:16.800
WHERE ROGER STIMPLE
USED TO WORK

27:17.100 --> 27:19.500
HAD A CONTRACT AT THE PARK
WHERE RUBY WAS FOUND.

27:19.800 --> 27:22.600
<i>COULDN'T YOU HAVE CALLED WITH
THIS INFORMATION, DETECTIVE?</i>

27:23.300 --> 27:24.200
MAY I COME IN?

27:26.200 --> 27:28.200
I'M NOT SURE
WHAT DAVID TOLD YOU.

27:29.000 --> 27:30.600
BUT HE KNOWS
WHAT HE DID WAS WRONG.

27:31.400 --> 27:33.100
WELL, THAT'S A START.

27:33.900 --> 27:36.700
PLEASE DO NOT LET THIS BE THE
LAST THING HE DOES AS A POLICE OFFICER.

27:36.700 --> 27:37.900
THAT MAY NOT BE UP TO ME.

27:38.900 --> 27:41.500
AS SOON AS THE SUSPECT SHOWS UP
IN COURT WITH HIS LAWYER,

27:42.000 --> 27:43.500
DAVID'S ACTIONS
ARE GONNA BE FRONT AND CENTER,

27:43.500 --> 27:45.700
AND THE ONLY WAY OUT OF THIS
IS GONNA BE FOR ME TO LIE.

27:47.600 --> 27:48.700
IS THAT
WHAT YOU WANT ME TO DO?

27:53.400 --> 27:54.100
YOU KNOW, I WONDER.

27:57.800 --> 27:59.300
WOULD YOU BE HERE
PLEADING DAVID'S CASE

27:59.300 --> 28:00.300
IF Y'ALL WEREN'T DATING?

28:00.300 --> 28:01.300
<i>BUT WE ARE DATING.</i>

28:01.300 --> 28:04.700
I DON'T WANT TO TALK ABOUT THAT.
I DON'T WANT TO DISCUSS IT.

28:14.400 --> 28:15.300
CHIEF...

28:16.100 --> 28:18.100
I KNOW THAT
YOU AND COMMANDER TAYLOR

28:18.600 --> 28:20.400
HAVE A COMPLICATED
RELATIONSHIP.

28:21.100 --> 28:23.000
BUT HE CARES A LOT
ABOUT DAVID,

28:23.900 --> 28:25.400
AND SOMETIMES...

28:26.100 --> 28:28.300
????

28:51.100 --> 28:53.700
CHIEF...WE CHECKED
STIMPLE'S HOME COMPUTER.

28:53.900 --> 28:56.900
NO SIGN OF PORNOGRAPHY --
CHILD OR OTHER.

28:57.400 --> 29:00.400
30-YEAR-OLD SINGLE MAN
LIVES ALONE -- NO PORNOGRAPHY.

29:00.400 --> 29:02.300
<i>NOW, THAT'S SUSPICIOUS.</i>

29:03.200 --> 29:05.700
CHIEF, ONE OF THE KEYS
ON ROGER'S KEY CHAIN

29:05.700 --> 29:07.700
MATCHES THE PADLOCK
ON THE FENCE AT THE PARK.

29:08.100 --> 29:09.300
BOOTS
FROM ROGER'S APARTMENT

29:09.300 --> 29:11.400
MATCH THE PRINTS WE FOUND
IN THE PARK'S BATHROOM.

29:11.400 --> 29:12.800
THAT'S PROBABLY
WHERE HE RAPED HER.

29:13.900 --> 29:16.400
ROGER'S DNA IS ON FILE
FROM PREVIOUS BUSTS.

29:16.400 --> 29:17.900
IT'LL TAKE A FEW DAYS
TO GET A MATCH.

29:18.200 --> 29:20.100
OKAY, WHAT ABOUT
THE TWO OTHER MISSING GIRLS?

29:20.300 --> 29:23.000
I'M CHECKING THEIR CASE FILES
AGAINST ROGER'S MERCURY

29:23.000 --> 29:24.400
AND HIS WHEREABOUTS
FIVE YEARS AGO.

29:24.600 --> 29:26.100
IF OUR SCUMBAG
KILLED THOSE GIRLS,

29:26.100 --> 29:27.900
HE PROBABLY BURIED THEM
IN THE PARK.

29:28.000 --> 29:29.800
HE KNOWS THE PLACE
INSIDE AND OUT.

29:30.100 --> 29:31.700
THEN WHY DIDN'T HE
BURY RUBY?

29:32.100 --> 29:34.100
HE PROBABLY PANICKED
WHEN HE HEARD OUR HELICOPTERS,

29:34.400 --> 29:35.500
LEFT HER IN THE DITCH.

29:35.500 --> 29:37.700
I'M TELLING YOU, CHIEF --
THOSE GIRLS ARE OUT THERE.

29:38.400 --> 29:41.200
GRIFFITH PARK
IS OVER 4,000 ACRES.

29:41.700 --> 29:43.500
WE'D NEVER FIND THEM
WITHOUT ROGER'S HELP.

29:43.500 --> 29:44.500
SO, WE GET HIM TO TELL US.

29:45.400 --> 29:46.400
IT'S NOT THAT SIMPLE.

29:46.700 --> 29:49.400
IT WORKED WITH RUBY. WHY NOT
WITH THESE PREVIOUS TWO GIRLS?

29:49.600 --> 29:50.900
GET GABRIEL,
HAVE HIM TALK TO HIM --

29:50.900 --> 29:54.000
IT'S NOT...THAT...SIMPLE.

29:54.000 --> 29:55.600
WELL, THEN,
WHAT AM I MISSING?

29:59.300 --> 30:00.200
EXCUSE ME, EVERYONE.

30:00.700 --> 30:01.600
I WANTED TO, UH,

30:02.400 --> 30:05.300
THANK ALL OF YOU PERSONALLY
FOR YOUR HARD WORK AND DEDICATION.

30:06.000 --> 30:06.900
I KNOW IT'S, UH...

30:08.300 --> 30:09.100
IT'S JUST AWFUL

30:09.100 --> 30:11.300
WHEN AN INVESTIGATION
ENDS THE WAY THIS ONE DID.

30:11.900 --> 30:14.200
PHD HANDLED IT QUICKLY,
PROFESSIONALLY,

30:14.700 --> 30:16.200
AND YOU GOT A PREDATOR
OFF THE STREET.

30:17.000 --> 30:18.100
THANK YOU,
CHIEF POPE.

30:19.500 --> 30:20.800
DO WE HAVE A BOOKING PHOTO
OF THE SUSPECT?

30:20.800 --> 30:22.300
I'D LIKE TO RELEASE IT
TO THE PRESS.

30:22.300 --> 30:25.900
UH...THERE'S BEEN
A...SLIGHT COMPLICATION.

30:27.100 --> 30:27.800
WHAT'S THAT?

30:29.200 --> 30:31.800
WELL, THERE'S SOME QUESTION
AS TO WHETHER ROGER'S CONFESSION

30:31.800 --> 30:33.700
<i>CAME AFTER HE INVOKED
HIS RIGHT TO COUNSEL.</i>

30:34.300 --> 30:36.300
I DON'T UNDERSTAND THAT.
IF HE INVOKED, HE INVOKED.

30:36.400 --> 30:37.900
<i>IF HE CONFESSED,
HE REVOKED, RIGHT?</i>

30:38.100 --> 30:39.700
UH, IT FELL
SOMEWHERE IN BETWEEN.

30:40.200 --> 30:42.900
AND, UNFORTUNATELY,
WE DIDN'T GET IT ON TAPE.

30:43.500 --> 30:46.400
IT DOESN'T HURT US TOO BAD,
BUT THE THING IS, CHIEF,

30:46.600 --> 30:48.600
WE THINK
THIS GUY ROGER'S RESPONSIBLE

30:48.600 --> 30:50.800
FOR AT LEAST
TWO OTHER CHILD ABDUCTIONS.

30:51.100 --> 30:54.600
WE DON'T WANT TO TAINT OTHER
WITNESSES BY RELEASING ROGER'S PHOTO.

30:54.800 --> 30:57.400
SO WE'RE GOING TO KEEP
HIS IDENTITY UNDER WRAPS

30:57.400 --> 30:59.900
UNTIL WE'RE DONE
WITH THE INVESTIGATION.

31:01.400 --> 31:02.000
OKAY. ALL RIGHT.

31:02.000 --> 31:03.800
BUT I WANT THIS SORTED OUT
BY THE TIME HE'S ARRAIGNED

31:03.800 --> 31:05.900
SO I CAN SMEAR HIS FACE
ALL OVER THE NEWS.

31:07.000 --> 31:09.900
COMMANDER TAYLOR AND I
ARE POOLING OUR RESOURCES.

31:10.800 --> 31:11.500
OKAY. GOOD.

31:12.100 --> 31:13.000
THANK YOU, COMMANDER.

31:16.600 --> 31:18.300
CHIEF JOHNSON,
YOU WANTED TO TALK?

31:20.900 --> 31:22.900
GABRIEL LET HIS EMOTIONS
GET THE BETTER OF HIM.

31:22.900 --> 31:24.600
IT'S HAPPENED
TO ALL OF US.

31:25.800 --> 31:28.400
WHAT GABRIEL DID WAS, UH...
IT WAS IMMATURE.

31:28.500 --> 31:29.700
IT WASN'T JUST IMMATURE.

31:30.800 --> 31:32.000
HE ACTED IN SUCH A WAY

31:32.000 --> 31:33.800
THAT I NOW CAN'T SEE
HOW TO CLOSE MY CASE

31:33.800 --> 31:36.200
WITHOUT PERMANENTLY DAMAGING
HIS CAREER.

31:36.500 --> 31:40.200
<i>AND MAKE NO MISTAKE, COMMANDER,
I WILL CLOSE MY CASE.</i>

31:40.200 --> 31:41.300
WHOA.

31:42.200 --> 31:45.000
LET'S NOT FORGET --
GABRIEL'S NOT THE BAD GUY HERE.

31:45.000 --> 31:46.700
THERE'S A CHILD KILLER
IN THE MIX.

31:46.700 --> 31:48.300
WHOSE ADMISSION
I CAN'T USE.

31:50.600 --> 31:52.800
TOO BAD YOU CAN'T GET ROGER
TO CONFESS AGAIN.

31:53.800 --> 31:54.500
BELIEVE ME...

31:55.700 --> 31:58.100
I'VE BEEN TRYING TO FIGURE OUT
HOW TO DO THAT ALL NIGHT.

32:00.900 --> 32:02.400
YOU HAVEN'T
BOOKED THE SUSPECT YET?

32:02.800 --> 32:04.600
NO. HE'S STILL
IN ISOLATION.

32:06.500 --> 32:07.900
YOU KNOW WHAT, CHIEF?

32:10.500 --> 32:11.800
YOU HAVE A LOT TO DO
STILL,

32:12.600 --> 32:16.300
WHAT WITH HAVING TO LOOK AFTER
THESE OTHER TWO MISSING GIRLS.

32:17.400 --> 32:19.400
WHY DON'T I TAKE ROGER
OFF YOUR HANDS?

32:19.900 --> 32:21.500
HAVE ROBBERY HOMICIDE
BOOK HIM.

32:23.800 --> 32:25.100
I DON'T SEE
HOW THAT'S GONNA HELP ME.

32:25.600 --> 32:27.600
OH...IT WILL.

32:29.700 --> 32:30.500
IT WILL.

32:48.400 --> 32:49.100
