33:02.500 --> 33:04.100
IT'LL TAKE WEEKS,
IF IT WORKS AT ALL.

33:05.100 --> 33:05.600
THANK YOU.

33:07.600 --> 33:09.500
CHIEF...UM...

33:17.300 --> 33:18.800
I DID A BAD THING ONCE.

33:20.500 --> 33:21.800
<i>I'M TALKING ABOUT
THE FIRST TIME.</i>

33:23.000 --> 33:24.100
IT WAS MANY YEARS AGO.

33:25.100 --> 33:27.000
I WAS VERY YOUNG,
LIKE GABRIEL,

33:27.800 --> 33:28.600
AND MY HEART --

33:30.500 --> 33:31.900
<i>BACK WHEN
I HAD A HEART --</i>

33:32.500 --> 33:33.600
WAS IN THE RIGHT PLACE.

33:34.800 --> 33:36.900
BUT I WAS STUBBORN,
I WAS STUPID, AND...

33:38.900 --> 33:40.900
I DID SOMETHING
THAT I'M NOT PROUD OF.

33:44.600 --> 33:45.200
BUT...

33:46.400 --> 33:48.100
PEOPLE GROW.

33:48.200 --> 33:49.600
PEOPLE CHANGE.

33:50.300 --> 33:51.000
AND...

33:52.900 --> 33:55.200
<i>WELL...
LOOK AT ME NOW.</i>

33:59.700 --> 34:02.000
EXCUSE ME, CHIEF.
WE JUST GOT A CALL FROM LOCKUP.

34:02.000 --> 34:03.400
ROGER WANTS TO TALK
TO YOU.

34:03.500 --> 34:04.200
<i>TO ME?</i>

34:04.300 --> 34:06.400
YES. COMMANDER TAYLOR'S
BRINGING HIM UP RIGHT NOW.

34:08.600 --> 34:10.100
I'M HERE
TO PROTECT AND SERVE.

34:10.100 --> 34:12.300
YOU'RE NOT PROTECTING ME.

34:12.400 --> 34:15.400
I WANTED YOU OUT OF THERE
SO YOU'D BE SAFE.

34:17.000 --> 34:18.000
WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

34:19.199 --> 34:19.900
WHAT HAPPENED?!

34:20.400 --> 34:21.400
HE DID THIS TO ME!

34:22.100 --> 34:24.199
HE PUT ME IN THE CELL
WITH OTHER PRISONERS!

34:24.699 --> 34:26.000
SOMETIMES YOU FORGET

34:26.000 --> 34:28.500
HOW OTHER PRISONERS
TREAT PEOPLE LIKE ROGER.

34:29.600 --> 34:31.100
HOW DID THEY FIND OUT
WHO HE WAS?

34:31.100 --> 34:34.600
I DON'T KNOW. MAYBE SOME GUARD
MUST HAVE SAID SOMETHING.

34:34.600 --> 34:37.800
ISN'T THERE A RULE AGAINST PUTTING
CHILD MOLESTERS IN GENERAL POPULATION?

34:38.199 --> 34:39.800
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.
WAIT A MINUTE.

34:39.800 --> 34:42.900
IS THAT WHAT YOU ARE, ROGER?
ARE YOU A CHILD MOLESTER?

34:42.900 --> 34:45.100
I DIDN'T --
'CAUSE BEFORE,YOU SAID YOU WEREN'T.

34:45.100 --> 34:47.100
YOU DENIED EVERYTHING.
WHAT'S IT GONNA BE?

34:47.300 --> 34:49.600
ARE YOU A CHILD MOLESTER
OR NOT?!

34:49.900 --> 34:53.100
WHAT ARE YOU, ROGER?!
DO YOU LIKE LITTLE GIRLS, HUH?!

34:53.199 --> 34:56.300
WHAT ARE YOU, ROGER?!
ARE YOU A CHILD MOLESTER?!

34:56.300 --> 34:57.600
HE TOLD THEM ABOUT ME!

34:57.600 --> 34:58.400
ALL RIGHT!

34:58.900 --> 35:00.800
MR. STIMPLE,
DO NOT ANSWER THAT QUESTION!

35:00.800 --> 35:02.200
COMMANDER, THAT'S ENOUGH.

35:06.000 --> 35:07.600
SORRY. SORRY, CHIEF.

35:10.100 --> 35:11.100
PLEASE HELP ME.

35:11.300 --> 35:12.900
<i>I CAN'T DO ANYTHING
FOR YOU!</i>

35:13.200 --> 35:14.300
I CAN'T EVEN TALK TO YOU,

35:14.300 --> 35:15.500
BECAUSE
YOU'VE ASKED FOR A LAWYER!

35:17.300 --> 35:18.400
I WANT TO TALK.

35:23.300 --> 35:24.000
OKAY.

35:25.000 --> 35:25.800
FINE.

35:27.400 --> 35:29.000
LET'S GET A DOCTOR
TO TAKE A LOOK AT YOU,

35:29.700 --> 35:30.700
AND THEN WE'LL TALK.

35:33.900 --> 35:35.900
NO. NOT HIM.

35:38.900 --> 35:40.500
CAN'T WE JUST
KEEP THIS WHITE?

35:46.400 --> 35:47.100
LET'S GO.

35:54.400 --> 35:55.200
<i>THANK YOU, DOCTOR.</i>

36:03.500 --> 36:06.900
<i>ROGER, JUST TO BE
PERFECTLY CLEAR,</i>

36:08.200 --> 36:10.300
<i>YOU ARE NOW SAYING
THAT YOU WANT TO TALK TO ME.</i>

36:10.400 --> 36:11.100
OUCH.

36:11.500 --> 36:12.500
<i>IN FACT, YOU ASKED TO TALK.</i>

36:12.500 --> 36:15.300
I HEARD HE HAD A LITTLE SCUFFLE
IN THE GENERAL POPULATION.

36:15.900 --> 36:18.800
HONESTLY, CHIEF, THERE WAS
NO SAFE PLACE TO PUT THIS GUY.

36:18.800 --> 36:21.200
<i>YOU DON'T HAVE TO TALK TO ME
WITHOUT YOUR ATTORNEY PRESENT.</i>

36:21.800 --> 36:23.000
<i>YOU UNDERSTAND THAT, TOO?</i>

36:23.400 --> 36:24.200
<i>UH-HUH.</i>

36:26.300 --> 36:27.000
<i>OKAY.</i>

36:28.500 --> 36:29.900
<i>AGAIN,
JUST FOR THE RECORD,</i>

36:31.000 --> 36:32.300
YOU WERE JUST TREATED
BY A DOCTOR

36:33.200 --> 36:34.900
FOR WOUNDS
YOU SAY YOU RECEIVED

36:34.900 --> 36:36.900
FROM YOUR FELLOW PRISONERS
IN YOUR HOLDING CELL.

36:37.200 --> 36:38.600
THEY ATTACKED
AND BEAT YOU.

36:38.600 --> 36:40.600
THEY'RE GONNA KILL ME!
THEY'RE GONNA KILL ME!

36:40.800 --> 36:42.100
I CAN'T GO BACK DOWN THERE!

36:42.100 --> 36:44.400
IT'S OKAY.
IT'S OKAY, ROGER.

36:44.400 --> 36:45.700
I WON'T SEND YOU BACK.

36:46.500 --> 36:48.800
I SWEAR.
YOU'RE SAFE WITH ME.

36:50.900 --> 36:54.900
AND I PROMISE YOU,
I WILL LOOK INTO WHOEVER DID TO YOU, OKAY?

36:56.300 --> 36:57.000
OKAY?

37:00.400 --> 37:01.000
ROGER...

37:03.100 --> 37:04.700
LET'S YOU AND I
TALK ABOUT RUBY.

37:07.200 --> 37:09.000
BECAUSE WE LOOKED FOR HER
BY THE PAY PHONES,

37:09.000 --> 37:09.900
BUT SHE WASN'T THERE.

37:15.100 --> 37:16.300
I WANT TO HELP Y'ALL
FIND HER.

37:18.300 --> 37:19.400
LOOK, I MADE A MISTAKE.

37:19.700 --> 37:21.300
I WAS WRONG
NOT TO TALK TO Y'ALL BEFORE.

37:21.900 --> 37:23.800
ALL I KNOW IS,
I WAS DRIVING THROUGH THE PARK,

37:23.800 --> 37:24.800
AND THERE SHE WAS,

37:26.100 --> 37:27.700
JUST WALKING ALONE,
BY HERSELF.

37:27.900 --> 37:28.600
IN THE PARK?

37:29.100 --> 37:29.700
YEAH.

37:30.500 --> 37:31.700
AND I USED TO WORK
IN THAT PARK.

37:31.700 --> 37:34.100
IT'S NOT SAFE FOR A KID
TO WALK AROUND ALONE LIKE THAT.

37:34.400 --> 37:35.900
SO I OFFERED HER A LIFT.

37:37.100 --> 37:38.900
THAT'S WHY YOUR DOGS
SMELLED HER IN MY VAN.

37:42.100 --> 37:43.500
SHE WANTED
TO CALL HER FOLKS.

37:44.200 --> 37:47.000
SO I-I TOOK A SERVICE ROAD
THAT I KNOW,

37:47.800 --> 37:48.900
AND I DROPPED HER OFF
BY THE PHONES.

37:48.900 --> 37:51.300
I GAVE HER SOME CHANGE
TO CALL HOME,

37:52.000 --> 37:53.100
AND THEN I TOOK OFF.

37:54.900 --> 37:57.400
I'M TELLING YOU,
THAT'S WHAT HAPPENED.

38:00.100 --> 38:02.800
DO YOU REMEMBER --
WAS SHE WEARING HER PINK JACKET?

38:04.300 --> 38:04.900
YEAH.

38:09.000 --> 38:10.100
YEAH, THAT SOUNDS RIGHT.

38:12.700 --> 38:14.000
SHE HAD HER HANDS
IN HER POCKETS.

38:15.400 --> 38:17.000
AND ABOUT WHAT TIME
WAS THIS?

38:18.500 --> 38:21.300
I THINK -- I THINK
IT WAS MAYBE AROUND 12:00.

38:22.000 --> 38:23.400
AND YOU NEVER
GOT OUT OF YOUR VAN?

38:24.000 --> 38:24.800
NO.

38:25.900 --> 38:27.000
THIS EXPLAINS A LOT --

38:27.800 --> 38:29.000
HOW SHE GOT IN YOUR VAN,

38:29.200 --> 38:31.000
WHY SHE WAS IN
THAT REMOTE PART OF THE PARK.

38:31.000 --> 38:33.600
YEAH. YEAH.
I WAS JUST TRYING TO HELP.

38:33.600 --> 38:35.900
AND YOU'RE HELPING NOW.
YOU'RE HELPING A LOT.

38:37.400 --> 38:39.200
BECAUSE, ROGER...

38:40.500 --> 38:43.900
...YOU'RE PROBABLY THE LAST
PERSON TO SEE RUBY ALIVE.

38:44.400 --> 38:46.000
YOU SEE, WE DIDN'T FIND HER
BY THE PAY PHONES,

38:46.000 --> 38:47.000
BUT WE DID FIND HER.

38:48.600 --> 38:49.800
SHE WAS DEAD, ROGER.

38:52.500 --> 38:53.200
OH, MAN.

38:55.300 --> 38:56.300
I CAN'T BELIEVE IT.

38:58.700 --> 39:00.400
DID YOU SEE ANYTHING SUSPICIOUS
IN THE PARK,

39:01.200 --> 39:04.500
A CAR THAT DIDN'T BELONG
OR SOMEONE WALKING AROUND?

39:07.200 --> 39:07.800
YEAH.

39:08.600 --> 39:10.200
YEAH, WELL, YOU KNOW,
THIS COULD BE NOTHING,

39:11.800 --> 39:14.400
BUT THERE WAS
THIS ONE DUDE I SAW

39:14.800 --> 39:16.000
AS WE WERE HEADING
TO THE PHONES.

39:17.600 --> 39:22.100
HE'S A YOUNG GUY,
MAYBE 20, 25.

39:23.000 --> 39:24.700
HE WAS BLACK OR HISPANIC.

39:24.700 --> 39:27.500
YOU KNOW, KIND OF CUBAN BLACK,
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

39:28.200 --> 39:29.100
HE'S A BIG GUY.

39:30.900 --> 39:31.500
OH, MAN.

39:34.200 --> 39:35.500
THERE ARE BAD PEOPLE
OUT THERE.

39:39.400 --> 39:40.000
ROGER...

39:41.200 --> 39:43.100
YOU SAY YOU SAW RUBY
IN THE PARK AROUND NOON.

39:43.900 --> 39:45.500
THAT'S WHEN HER TEACHERS
SAW HER LEAVING SCHOOL.

39:47.300 --> 39:47.900
WELL...

39:48.000 --> 39:49.500
THE SAME TIME
WE GOT PICTURES

39:49.500 --> 39:51.400
<i>OF YOUR VAN
DRIVING IN HER NEIGHBORHOOD.</i>

39:51.400 --> 39:52.100
I DRIVE ALL AROUND.

39:52.100 --> 39:53.600
YOU SAY YOU DIDN'T
GET OUT OF YOUR VAN,

39:54.000 --> 39:56.000
BUT WE'VE GOT
YOUR FOOTPRINTS ALL OVER.

39:56.000 --> 39:57.000
THAT DOESN'T
MEAN ANYTHING!

39:57.000 --> 39:59.200
AND YOU SAY YOU SAW RUBY
IN HER PINK JACKET,

39:59.800 --> 40:03.400
WHICH WE FOUND IN THE ALLEYWAY
WHERE SHE WAS ABDUCTED.

40:04.400 --> 40:06.300
NOW, IT IS HIGH TIME
THAT YOU TELL ME THE TRUTH.

40:08.800 --> 40:09.900
THE WHOLE TRUTH, ROGER.

40:11.700 --> 40:12.300
PLEASE.

40:14.200 --> 40:15.700
LET'S YOU AND I
HELP EACH OTHER.

40:18.200 --> 40:19.000
OTHERWISE...

40:19.800 --> 40:21.100
THERE'S NOTHING LEFT
TO TALK ABOUT.

40:29.400 --> 40:31.300
ALL RIGHT. I'M GONNA GO FIND
COMMANDER TAYLOR.

40:31.300 --> 40:34.100
- NO!DON'T SEND ME BACK THERE!
- WHAT CHOICE DO I HAVE?!

40:35.600 --> 40:37.800
IT'S SO HARD.

40:40.400 --> 40:41.000
LOOK.

40:41.800 --> 40:42.600
ROGER.

40:43.400 --> 40:46.500
YOU AGREED TO TALK TO ME.
THAT'S AN IMPORTANT FIRST STEP.

40:47.000 --> 40:48.600
NOW LET ME HELP YOU
MAKE THE NEXT ONE.

40:48.800 --> 40:51.800
BECAUSE I KNOW -- I KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE GOING THROUGH.

40:52.900 --> 40:54.100
'CAUSE GIRLS THAT AGE...

40:56.300 --> 40:58.200
THEY ARE SO BEAUTIFUL.

41:03.400 --> 41:06.700
OTHER GUYS, THEY PRETEND THAT
THEY DON'T FEEL THE SAME WAY,

41:06.900 --> 41:07.600
BUT THEY DO.

41:10.900 --> 41:12.300
AND THE GIRLS WANT IT,
TOO.

41:15.000 --> 41:16.300
THEY JUST CAN'T ADMIT IT...

41:18.700 --> 41:20.400
BECAUSE THEIR MOTHERS
WOULD PASS JUDGMENT.

41:22.000 --> 41:23.700
BUT I'M NOT
PASSING JUDGMENT, ROGER.

41:26.200 --> 41:27.500
I JUST WANT TO KNOW
WHAT HAPPENED.

41:32.800 --> 41:34.000
I WAS DRIVING AROUND,

41:35.800 --> 41:37.400
AND I SEEN THIS GIRL
I SEEN BEFORE.

41:38.800 --> 41:40.100
YOU COULDN'T HELP
BUT NOTICE HER.

41:41.600 --> 41:43.100
AND I DON'T GO FOR GIRLS
WHO DON'T WANT ME.

41:45.000 --> 41:47.100
I'VE BEEN ON THE OTHER END
OF THAT THING WHEN I WAS A KID.

41:48.500 --> 41:50.100
NO. SHE'S INTO IT.

41:50.600 --> 41:52.300
ALL YOU WERE DOING
WAS GIVING HER A RIDE.

41:52.300 --> 41:53.200
EXACTLY.

41:54.600 --> 41:55.800
WE WERE JUST
DRIVING AROUND.

41:57.000 --> 41:58.200
IT WAS ALL JUST FUN,
YOU KNOW?

41:59.700 --> 42:00.900
I WASN'T GONNA DO ANYTHING.

42:02.400 --> 42:03.400
BUT SHE WANTED IT.

42:04.500 --> 42:05.300
SO...

42:06.200 --> 42:07.400
SHE WAS FLIRTING
WITH YOU.

42:09.800 --> 42:10.900
YOU TWO FOOL AROUND?

42:15.600 --> 42:17.300
THEN RIGHT IN THE MIDDLE OF IT,
SHE CHANGED.

42:22.300 --> 42:23.300
SHE GOT ALL MAD AT ME.

42:25.300 --> 42:27.000
SAID SHE WAS GONNA TELL THE COPS
WHAT WE DONE.

42:28.800 --> 42:30.300
WHICH IS SO PERFECT --

42:32.000 --> 42:35.500
JUST LEAD ME ON AND...
THEN JUST FLIP LIKE THAT.

42:39.100 --> 42:40.000
AND I GOT MAD.

42:41.600 --> 42:42.400
ROGER...

42:43.500 --> 42:44.500
IF SOMETHING HAPPENED --

42:45.200 --> 42:47.600
IF THERE WAS AN ACCIDENT,
YOU NEED TO TELL ME.

42:48.800 --> 42:49.700
'CAUSE THE DNA...

42:50.900 --> 42:52.200
THAT'S GONNA LINK YOU
TO RUBY,

42:53.700 --> 42:55.800
AND THE D.A.'s GONNA
MAKE YOU OUT TO BE A MONSTER

42:55.800 --> 42:58.000
<i>IN A VERY PUBLIC TRIAL.</i>

42:59.500 --> 43:01.300
IS THAT HOW YOU WANT
YOUR MOTHER TO SEE YOU?

43:03.000 --> 43:05.000
IS THAT HOW YOU WANT
THE WORLD TO SEE YOU?

43:06.900 --> 43:10.900
<i>I KNOW THAT THERE'S AN
EXPLANATION THAT ONLY YOU HAVE,</i>

43:10.900 --> 43:13.300
AND I WANT TO HEAR
YOUR SIDE OF THE STORY.

43:14.100 --> 43:16.800
BUT IF I'M GONNA HELP YOU,
I NEED TO HEAR IT FROM YOU.

43:24.600 --> 43:26.900
SHE JUST STARTED
SCREAMING.

43:28.200 --> 43:30.500
SHE WAS MAKING
SO MUCH NOISE.

43:33.600 --> 43:35.900
I WAS JUST TRYING
TO KEEP HER QUIET.

43:39.500 --> 43:40.800
I DIDN'T WANT
